name: Proximo - Gloria
description:
Gloria, the 2nd artwork from Proximo Series dedicated and made for all my respective collectors. It's clear that all supports i've received until this day, this moment, is beyond everything.

Gloria stands for every spirits, every energy we all had and given to make our dreams come true. Although we all faced many different obstacles and life-barriers, i'd really really hope that may your life and your beloved ones have a beautiful moment in the coming days.

No matter where you're came from, your economy status, your major, your race, and every diversity we got, i wish you all the best.

It's an honour to be a part of this life-changing process and to be able to share my perspective to the world.

From Boogie Bronson with love.
